(1. Scope) Tj
72 638 Td
(This document defines system-level requirements for the Battery Management System \(BMS\)) Tj
72 624 Td
(developed by Vertex Systems GmbH for integration into the Helios Automotive AG NOVA platform.) Tj
72 610 Td
(The BMS monitors and controls a 400 V lithium-ion battery pack for electric vehicles.) Tj
72 596 Td
(Applicable standards: ISO 26262:2018, IEC 61851-1:2017, AUTOSAR R22-11, ISO 9001:2015.) Tj
72 582 Td
(This specification is the baseline for FMEA document NOVA-FMEA-004.) Tj
72 568 Td
(Interface definitions are provided separately in NOVA-IRS-002.) Tj
72 554 Td
() Tj
72 540 Td
(2. System Overview) Tj
72 526 Td
(Nominal pack voltage: 400 VDC. Max charge voltage: 450 VDC.) Tj
72 512 Td
(Operating temperature range: -40 degrees C to +85 degrees C.) Tj
ET

